Technical stuff

From my linkedIn profile page "About" section. Home Project #1 - my free HTML app TECHNICAL HIGHLIGHTS OF THE APP igotostars.org - totally self-contained app in one single HTML file (12MB) - free and open source - github > igotostars - app is responsive - it runs on desktops, laptops, tablets and phones - after loading into your web browser, the app never accesses the internet - Saved as "WebPage, HTML only", and then double-clicked on, the app will run fine on a device having no internet connection

 

from igotostars.org
HELP PAGE
for click-on-a-year

 
 

Quick Start

Look for times when the graph goes BELOW the red stress line into the red zones. When the graph stays BELOW the red stress line for a few weeks or months, then challenging stress is much more likely to happen.

It's all about the RED STRESS LINE.

 

Influences during the Year

Each influence (also called aspect) has a beginning date and an ending date.

Hills and Valleys

Favorable influences appear as a hill
Challenging influences appear as a valley

All of the hills and valleys for every influence are combined into the final shape of the graph for the year

 

WHAT!
No Tall Dark Handsome Stranger?

igotostars is not like a fortune-teller.

 

igotostars shows when during the year you are
MORE LIKELY to have stress ...

 

or LESS LIKELY to have stress.

 
Does igotostars tell exactly
what is going to happen?

No.

 
Does igotostars measure
stress levels over time?

Yes it does.

 

The score for the year

Score Numbers
 

Scores go from 1 to 99.
- a score of 88 is more favorable than
88% of all scores in the world
- a score of 11 is more favorable than
11% of all scores in the world
This type of score is called a PERCENTILE RANK.

 
Score Meaning
 
 

A Yearly score tells how likely it is that the person has challenging stress AT SOME TIME during the year.

- Higher scores (green) are good - Lower scores (red) are challenging

 
Overcome stressful times
 

by using your FREE WILL

 
 
 

all available reports
in igotostars.org

 

The first page has a list of people already entered.
You can switch to a list of groups, already entered.
Click or tap on a person or group to do the reports.

You can add the birth information of new people.
